 every hour using a time-weighted average premium between the perpetual contract price and the underlying index. The exchange's order book model on Sui blockchain enables fast settlement of funding payments between long and short positions. Funding rates are determined by the 8-hour TWAP of the premium, then divided by 8 for hourly payments. Bluefin's institutional-grade matching engine ensures accurate price discovery for funding rate calculations."}]]}],"$Lf",["$L10","$L11","$L12"],"$L13"]}],"$L14"]}]]}]
